humbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fdf%2FStarship_Troopers_-_movie_poster.jpg&h=49b846a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/1024x576/201809/20180914135740_1_cover2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2F1024x576%2F201809%2F20180914135740_1_cover2.jpg&h=6715063b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述五名好朋友在每年5月都會玩起鬼抓人的遊戲，以維持彼此的友誼。而當他們當中最厲害的傑瑞（Jerry）將要結婚時，另外四人本以為這是能打敗他的方法，但未料，對方卻早已做好萬全的準備<br />\n<br />\n3.故事講述在23世紀，人類與外星昆蟲間的星際戰爭。在地球向外星昆蟲宣戰的一年前，Johnny Rico於布宜諾斯艾利斯就讀高中，期間與另一女同學Carmen相戀。在高中畢業後，Johnny的父親希望兒子升讀哈佛大學，但Johnny眼見Carmen投考軍校，為了追求Carmen，Johnny惟有跟從。軍校根據他們的學業成績，Johnny被編往步兵隊，而Carmen則被編入飛行學校。受訓期間，一位名為Dizzy的高中女同學，同為Johnny在校橄欖球隊的戰術教練，對Johnny仰慕多時，也加入了步兵隊。Carmen成績優異，被提前選為宇宙母艦Rodger Young「羅傑&middot;楊」號副駕駛，與Johnny高.......<br />\n<br />\n4.一晃十年過去，地球人和虫族的戰爭如火如荼，愈演愈烈。某日，空軍元帥奧瑪&middot;阿諾克（斯蒂芬&middot;霍根Stephen Hog​​an 飾）來地球人的遠方農場羅庫山視察，時任上校的強尼&middot;瑞哥（加斯帕&middot;範&middot;迪恩Casper Van Dien 飾）也一同前來。在此期間，阿諾克的心智被蟲王操控，他切斷了隔離區的電力，使基地完全失去保護。是夜，虫族對隔離區發動總攻，地球軍雖頑強抵抗，終因寡不敵眾而告敗，基地淪陷。阿諾克則和一干心腹逃離，飛船迫降在OM-1行星........<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *薯片版無字幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Ycq1ntVhL2qxiUbHFcPlBEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1193076c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Ycq1ntVhL2qxiUbHFcPlBEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a7aa7dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c778d962fcfbc4846705566533982225dccd9fb6","tid":822500,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e20b478523f203b8f1572e94b2893ae22642c9","tid":822500,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77989f4a17c8e74db139f74e89d4dd2924807a0","tid":822500,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5b00d1a5a032d66454951e2d5fc36e2d14f20e","tid":822500,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a551ba1646b86d9a3ea0c3c7a50e7ef154527087","tid":822500,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaae3dc8bff5c23ed2f6714ffe5ffadf43cbceb","tid":822500,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71e3a54ba14af83d8033e4a8bff9b7ab717883c","tid":822500,"uid":29160